(Where are the juvenile cows full of curiosity going?)

1010
00:40:23,990 --> 00:40:25,129
- They...
- Well...

1011
00:40:25,130 --> 00:40:26,130
The child doesn't like it.

1012
00:40:26,131 --> 00:40:27,329
- The baby.
- No.

1013
00:40:27,330 --> 00:40:28,330
Now...

1014
00:40:29,300 --> 00:40:32,270
The cows escaped from the ranch.

1015
00:40:33,770 --> 00:40:34,870
For real?

1016
00:40:36,540 --> 00:40:38,370
I think the cows left the range.

1017
00:40:38,940 --> 00:40:40,910
Is someone there to take care of them?

1018
00:40:41,380 --> 00:40:43,039
- What?
- The outside door...

1019
00:40:43,040 --> 00:40:44,150
But I clearly tied it shut.

1020
00:40:47,020 --> 00:40:48,980
Did the knot come loose?

1021
00:40:50,090 --> 00:40:51,850
The rope must've come undone.

1022
00:40:52,120 --> 00:40:53,249
Shouldn't you go over?

1023
00:40:53,250 --> 00:40:54,920
No, I'll tell someone to take care of it.

1024
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:58,189
Hey, Tae Joon is there, right?

1025
00:40:58,190 --> 00:41:01,530
The cows have escaped. The big range in front of the warehouse.

1026
00:41:03,430 --> 00:41:05,570
- Yes, take care of it.
- Okay.

1027
00:41:06,170 --> 00:41:08,399
That area is an easy place to herd the cows back in.

1028
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:09,639
(On the phone with his brother)

1029
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:10,769
- Leading the cows back in...
- Please go there...

1030
00:41:10,770 --> 00:41:11,909
- isn't hard over there.
- and check it out.

1031
00:41:11,910 --> 00:41:13,680
- Yes, just gather them up.
- Over there.

1032
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:15,379
Your second son?

1033
00:41:15,380 --> 00:41:16,540
Yes.

1034
00:41:16,850 --> 00:41:20,150
(Putting faith in his second son and digging back into lunch)

1035
00:41:21,050 --> 00:41:23,990
(Meanwhile, at the farm)

1036
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:29,190
(Camerawork as if it's a scene from a disaster film)

1037
00:41:31,660 --> 00:41:33,930
The cows escaped!

1038
00:41:34,100 --> 00:41:36,770
(The production crew runs over at the news of the escaped cows.)

1039
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:41,569
